  ### TRIPS and ACTIVITIES ###
  /trips (User's trips -- also the default logged in page)
    /trips/new
    /trips/:trip_id (Individual trip page)
    /trips/:trip_id/update
    /trips/:trip_id/delete
        /trips/:trip_id/activity/new
        /trips/:trip_id/activity/:activity_id (Individual activity page)
        /trips/:trip_id/activity/:activity_id/update
        /trips/:trip_id/activity/:activity_id/delete

  ### USERS ###    
  /profile/:user_id (User/friend's profile)
